item.title: Sinigang na Hipon at Isda
item.description: Seafoods stew of fish, shrimp, talbos ng kamote (sweet potato young leaves), tomatoes, ginger, mild green chili and onions. INGREDIENTS: 1 kg pork belly (cut into thick strips) 1 head of garlic (cruched, peeled and chooped) 1⁄2 cup vinegar 1⁄2 cup water salt and black pepper to taste Fresh sweet potato tops Fresh sweet potato tops
